   SOC-U.S.-IRAN (Lyon) _ Iran beats U.S., 2-1. By Alex Yannis.
</P>
<P>
   (We plan to move this story by 9 p.m. ET in `s' news file.)
</P>
<P>
   2-column hed.
</P>
<P>
   IRAN-POLITICS (Tehran) _ Iran's hardline Parliament impeaches
the moderate interior minister; but President Mohammad Khatami
names him a vice president. By Elaine Sciolino.
</P>
<P>
   (We plan to move this story by 9 p.m. ET in `i' news file.)
