cumulative perpetual preferred, Ba3/BB(MINUS)/---. Morgan Stanley
Dean Witter.
</P>
<P>
   US West Capital Funding, $2 billion of notes in four parts
consisting of 4-year, 7-year, 10-year and 30-year notes,
